exercise.statement:
  What can you say about A if U = \{1, 2, 3, 4, 5\}, B = \{2, 3\}, and (separately) 
(a) A \cup B = \{1, 2, 3,4\} 
(b) A \cap  B = \{2\} 
(c) A \oplus  B = \{3, 4, 5\}


